[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     38[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - Encryption row covers SSE-KMS for S3, DynamoDB at rest (default), encrypted EBS volumes for SageMaker training and inference, KMS-encrypted SageMaker output, and explicitly elevated KMS encryption for CloudWatch log groups. The CloudWatch log-group KMS callout is recipe-distinct and correctly identifies a frequently-missed surface.
