[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    107[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Finding A3: Procedure-driven SKU `usage_rate = mean(quantity / scheduled_cases)` is fragile to zero-case days and ignores per-procedure-type variation.**
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    108[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
